Package org.drools.planner.examples.ras2012

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Directed
    Class implementing this interface signifies that the represented entity has a sense of direction, namely eastbound or westbound.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    Main class for the application.
    CLI
    Command-line interface for the app.
    ProblemSolution
    This class represents the problem at hand.
    ScoreCalculator
    A class that converts a solution into a score, in order to be able to rank various solutions based on their efficiency.
    Visualizable
    States that the entity represented by the extending class knows how to render itself into an image.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CLI.ApplicationMode
    The modes that the application supports running in.
